4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper may involve numerical methods for estimating the ersatz quantities from time-averaged probability distributions. 
5. cs.ST (Statistics): The paper involves statistical analysis of non-stationary processes, which could potentially fall under the scope of statistics.
